    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Older car in poor overall condition and being listed honestly as a project, fixer-upper, or possible parts candidate. Expect significant cosmetic wear throughout, including tired paint, visible blemishes, worn interior surfaces, and general age-related deterioration. It does not present as a clean daily driver and should be assumed to need repairs, reconditioning, and deferred maintenance before being relied on regularly. Best suited for a buyer who wants a budget project, needs parts, or is comfortable taking on a vehicle that will require substantial attention.",
