      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, straightforward, and full of potential, this vehicle is a smart choice for a budget-conscious buyer seeking dependable basic transportation or a practical project. It shows its age and is best suited for someone who values value over perfection, but it offers an accessible entry point with plenty of utility left to give. An honest, no-nonsense opportunity at a very approachable price.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with some potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it does have plenty of life left for the right buyer who wants a cheap runabout, a project, or a solid parts car. It\u2019s being priced to sell and could be a great fit for someone handy who doesn\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC. If you want something honest, budget-friendly, and worth a look, send me a message.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Driver-grade project with solid enthusiast appeal. The engine starts, runs, and delivers usable power, and the chassis still has the kind of mechanical feel that makes these worth saving. It shows its age cosmetically and will need sorting, but the fundamentals make it a strong candidate for a budget build, weekend wrenching project, or parts donor with real value left in the package. If you want an affordable entry point into a rewarding platform with good bones and plenty of upside, this is a compelling buy.",
      "price": 5800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car fast. Not pretty, but it gets the job done. Priced to move.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "If you appreciate a car with a little grit and a lot of story, this one has the kind of personality you can\u2019t fake. It\u2019s an honest, road-worn machine with a lived-in charm that makes it feel approachable, practical, and ready for someone who sees potential instead of polish. Perfect as a budget-friendly runabout, a first project, or a dependable extra set of wheels, it offers the rare chance to get into something affordable with real character. Not flashy\u2014just straightforward, usable, and waiting for its next chapter.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers straightforward transportation at an accessible price point. A practical choice for buyers seeking dependable basic mobility, it delivers strong value for the money and a chance to own a vehicle without stretching the budget. If you want an honest, affordable car with plenty of usefulness left, this one deserves a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    }
